            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>15.2</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <sparkle:hardwareRequirements>arm64</sparkle:hardwareRequirements>
            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[## What's new

- Removed transcription vocabulary prompts because they could inject configured terms into dictation even when those words were not spoken.
- Transcriptions now use the original unbiased request behavior again.
]]></description>
